name: Stuffed (TinyJustice24)
description:
Stuffed is a fun eating competition styled game. 

Get your fill in this fun eating competition! Stuff your mouth until there just is just no more space, then chew like there is no tomorrow!

You must eat as much food as possible to get a new highscore! See if you can beat your friends on our leaderboard, to be the reigning champion of the food eating competition!
